{"type":"text","timestamp":1781151864443,"sessionID":"ses_14b140814ffe4N8PH7Vn6Su76Z","part":{"id":"prt_eb4ec9620001zV1bpALqaDcJeX","messageID":"msg_eb4ec572c001X3TK4L305FgIDR","sessionID":"ses_14b140814ffe4N8PH7Vn6Su76Z","type":"text","text":"The workflow contract confirms this is command-owned fan-out; I’m treating this invocation as the lineage execution phase, not spawning nested agents or external loops. I’ll create lineage-local state, iteration, dashboard, resource-map, and report artifacts only under `review/lineages/gpt-1`.","time":{"start":1781151864352,"end":1781151864442},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0aecb300b5d977ec016a2a38785910819182cc14725cc910a5","phase":"commentary"}}}}
